org.pistoiaalliance.helm.HELMSimilarityLibrary.gui.app

Class SimilaritySearchTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.concurrent.FutureTask<V>
      • javafx.concurrent.Task<Integer>
        • org.pistoiaalliance.helm.HELMSimilarityLibrary.gui.app.SimilaritySearchTask
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable, Future<Integer>, RunnableFuture<Integer>, javafx.concurrent.Worker<Integer>, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class SimilaritySearchTask
extends javafx.concurrent.Task<Integer>
    SimilaritySearch class to perform the algorithm of calculating the similarity of a query helm notation and a database of more helm notations in the following steps

    1. Calculation of the fingerprint of the query notation

    2. Calculation of the fingerprints of the notations in database

    3. Calculation of tanimoto of the query notation and every other notation

    4. Checking for subset in database

    5a. Returning the notations with a specified minimum similarity in descending order.

    5b. Or returning the notations that the query notation is a subset of.

    Author:
    bueltel
